# GraphQL endpoint of agent-platform-backend.
#
# Auth uses the httpOnly `ap_session` cookie (LLD-12), and a SameSite=Lax cookie
# is only sent on SAME-ORIGIN requests. So point this at a same-origin path and
# let the Vite dev proxy forward it to the backend (see vite.config.ts) — do NOT
# use an absolute cross-origin URL like http://localhost:8080/query, or the
# cookie won't be sent and you'll be logged out on every request.
#
# Default (recommended for dev + prod-behind-nginx): same-origin /query.
VITE_GRAPHQL_ENDPOINT=/query
